place will meet your expectations, requirements, or satisfaction, or that any errors or defects will be corrected. No advice or information, whether oral or written, obtained by you from the marketplace, TrekGuider inc., or through the marketplace shall create any warranty, representation, covenant, or guarantee not expressly and explicitly stated in these terms and conditions.</p>',

