sted, transmitted, or otherwise made available by you on or through the marketplace; (c) your violation, breach, or non-compliance with these terms and conditions, any applicable marketplace policies, or any applicable law, statute, ordinance, regulation, or administrative rule; (d) your violation, infringement, or misappropriation of any rights of another party, including, but not limited to, intellectual property rights, proprietary rights, contractual rights, or privacy rights; or (e) any and all disputes, controversies, or claims of any nature whatsoever between you and another user of the marketplace, or between you and any third party, arising from, relating to, or connected with the marketplace or your use thereof. This indemnification obligation shall survive any termination or expiration of these terms and conditions and your use of the marketplace.</p>',

