g, transaction fees, commission structures, revenue sharing arrangements, refund policies, chargeback procedures, subscription terms, billing practices, and all other financial and transactional aspects of the Marketplace platform.<br>·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Copyright Policy:</strong> The Marketplace\'s comprehensive and controlling Copyright Policy, as amended, revised, or updated from time to time, which meticulously establishes and comprehensively governs the Marketplace\'s policies, practices, and procedures regarding intellectual property rights, copyright protection, Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA) compliance, procedures for reporting and addressing copyright infringement claims, counter-notification mechanisms, and related legal and regulatory requirements pertaining to copyrighted content and intellectual property on the Marketplace platform.<br>·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Dispute Resolution Policy:</strong> The Marketplace\'s comprehensive and controlling Dispute Resolution Policy, as amended, revised, or updated from time to time, which meticulously sets forth and comprehensively governs the Marketplace\'s policies, practices, and procedures regarding the resolution of disputes, controversies, and claims of any kind or nature whatsoever arising between users of the Marketplace, or between users and the Marketplace, including, but not limited to, dispute escalation protocols, mediation procedures, arbitration provisions, forum selection clauses, governing law provisions, and limitations on available remedies and legal recourse.<br>·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Seller Agreement:</strong> The Marketplace\'s comprehensive and controlling Seller Agreement, as amended, revised, or updated from time to time, which meticulously delineates and comprehensively governs the legally binding contractual relationship, rights, obligations, responsibilities, liabilities, limitations, restrictions, and disclaimers applicable to sellers, 