reto, and not by or on behalf of any third-party, whether claiming as a purported third-party beneficiary, assignee, transferee, or other claimant lacking direct contractual privity with TrekGuider Inc. under these Terms and Conditions.</p>',

      'paragraph-19' => '<h2><strong>19. Contact Information</strong></h2><p>For any and all questions, inquiries, concerns, complaints, requests for clarification, or other communications pertaining to these Terms and Conditions, the TrekGuider Marketplace, its services, functionalities, or operations, or to exercise any of your rights or fulfill any of your obligations under these Terms and Conditions or applicable law, you are explicitly directed and required to contact TrekGuider Inc. through the following designated and officially authorized communication channels and contact methods exclusively:<br>·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Designated Email Addresses for Specific Inquiries:</strong><br>o&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Legal and Policy-Related Inquiries, including DMCA Notices and Legal Process:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">legal@trekguider.com</span> (for formal legal correspondence, policy-related inquiries, requests for legal interpretation, service of legal process, and submission of Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA) infringement notifications and counter-notifications).<br>o&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Copyright-Specific Inquiries and Intellectual Property Matters:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">copyright@trekguider.com</span> (for all communications, inquiries, and reports specifically and exclusively pertaining to copyright infringement, intellectual property rights violations, and related matters).<br>o&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>General Inquiries, Customer Support, and all other Non-Legal or Non-Copyright Related Communications:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">contact@trekguider.com</span> (for all routine inquiries, customer support requests, technical assistance, account-related issues, general feedback, and any and all other communications not specifically requiring legal or copyright-specific attention).<br>·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Official Website Contact Form:</strong> Electronic sub